{"word":"ἀνειλέω","slug":"ἀνειλέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνειλέω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to roll up together:—</i> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to crowd</i> or <i>throng together</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>ἀνείλω</el>, <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to shrink up</i> or <i>back</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}